SQL: SELECT "date_dim"."d_fy_quarter_seq", "item"."i_size", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "store_sales"."ss_sold_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "store_sales"."ss_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE "store_sales"."ss_promo_sk" IN (51, 79, 100, 15, 143, 96, 313, 150, 104, 343, 130, 286) AND "item"."i_brand" = 'edu packedu pack #2' GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_fy_quarter_seq", "item"."i_size" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_fy_quarter_seq", "item"."i_size";

SELECT "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk", "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns"  WHERE "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" IN (5, 3, 26, 29, 32, 16, 34, 28, 1, 33, 20, 35, 15, 18, 25, 9, 30) AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_return_quantity" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%1%2.0%' GROUP BY "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk", "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" ORDER BY "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk", "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_year", "item"."i_units", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_sales"."ws_sold_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_site" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_site"."web_open_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "web_sales"."ws_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE CAST("item"."i_category" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%Sport%s%' AND "item"."i_manufact" IN ('ationbarable', 'ationeseought', 'ationationable', 'eingcally', 'priantiable', 'callyoughtought', 'oughtoughtpri', 'antin stable', 'oughtation', 'ableationable', 'prioughtpri', 'prin stought', 'oughtn stought') AND CAST("web_site"."web_rec_end_date" AS varchar) LIKE '%2000-08-15%' GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_year", "item"."i_units" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_year", "item"."i_units";

SELECT "customer_address"."ca_suite_number", "customer_address"."ca_zip", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer_address"  WHERE "customer_address"."ca_street_number" IS NOT NULL AND CAST("customer_address"."ca_suite_number" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%4%20%' GROUP BY "customer_address"."ca_suite_number", "customer_address"."ca_zip" ORDER BY "customer_address"."ca_suite_number", "customer_address"."ca_zip";

SELECT "inventory"."inv_warehouse_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "inventory" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "inventory"."inv_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE ("item"."i_manufact_id" = 18 OR ("item"."i_manufact_id" IN (297, 277, 71, 272, 18, 153, 331) AND "item"."i_manufact_id" = 18)) AND CAST("item"."i_rec_end_date" AS varchar) LIKE '%2000-%10-26%' GROUP BY "inventory"."inv_warehouse_sk" ORDER BY "inventory"."inv_warehouse_sk";

SELECT "web_returns"."wr_returned_date_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns"  WHERE CAST("web_returns"."wr_return_ship_cost" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.0%' AND "web_returns"."wr_returned_date_sk" IN (2451285, 2452385, 2452375, 2451667, 2451664, 2451654, 2451295) AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_return_tax" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.%0%' AND "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk" = 4020 AND (CAST("web_returns"."wr_reversed_charge" AS varchar) LIKE '%0%.0%' OR CAST("web_returns"."wr_refunded_cash" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.%0%') GROUP BY "web_returns"."wr_returned_date_sk" ORDER BY "web_returns"."wr_returned_date_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_page"."wp_access_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "customer"."c_first_shipto_date_sk"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_first_name" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%Rob%ert%' AND "date_dim"."d_holiday" = 'Y';

SELECT "store_returns"."sr_store_sk", "store_returns"."sr_return_quantity", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_returns"  GROUP BY "store_returns"."sr_store_sk", "store_returns"."sr_return_quantity" ORDER BY "store_returns"."sr_store_sk", "store_returns"."sr_return_quantity";
SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_sales"  WHERE "store_sales"."ss_sold_date_sk" = 2451176 AND "store_sales"."ss_hdemo_sk" IN (1423);

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "household_demographics" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "customer"."c_current_hdemo_sk"  WHERE (CAST("household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%20%' OR ("household_demographics"."hd_dep_count" IN (7, 1, 5, 0, 8) AND "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" IN (19, 6, 13, 16))) AND "customer"."c_birth_country" IS NOT NULL AND ("household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count" != 0 OR "household_demographics"."hd_buy_potential" != '>10000' OR "household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count" IN (4, -1, 1)) AND "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk" IN (6706, 5304, 135, 1726, 4974, 362, 3726, 1408, 3081, 1232, 7143, 5224, 6170, 4970);

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "time_dim" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "time_dim"."t_time_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_sold_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "promotion" ON "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" = "promotion"."p_promo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk"  WHERE ("time_dim"."t_hour" IN (14) OR "time_dim"."t_hour" IN (1, 19, 18, 4, 11, 7, 16, 3, 17, 9, 5, 0, 2, 8, 13) OR CAST("time_dim"."t_hour" AS varchar) LIKE '%1%5%') AND CAST("web_sales"."ws_coupon_amt" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.0%';

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "web_sales"."ws_bill_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_sales"."ws_sold_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "web_sales"."ws_sold_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk"  WHERE "customer_address"."ca_location_type" = 'apartment' AND CAST("time_dim"."t_sub_shift" AS varchar) LIKE '%eveni%ng%' AND CAST("customer_address"."ca_county" AS varchar) LIKE '%Washington%' AND CAST("customer_address"."ca_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%M%ount%';

SELECT "customer"."c_first_sales_date_sk", "customer"."c_preferred_cust_flag", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_first_name" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%William%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_first_sales_date_sk", "customer"."c_preferred_cust_flag" ORDER BY "customer"."c_first_sales_date_sk", "customer"."c_preferred_cust_flag";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_week_seq", "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sq_ft", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer_address" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_addr_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "call_center" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" = "call_center"."cc_call_center_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "warehouse" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" = "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk"  WHERE "customer"."c_first_name" IN ('Richard', 'Donald', 'Elizabeth', 'Joseph', 'Michael', 'Thomas', 'Christopher', 'Linda', 'Charles', 'John', 'Jennifer', 'Robert', 'William') OR "customer"."c_last_name" = 'Garcia' GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_week_seq", "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sq_ft" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_week_seq", "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sq_ft";

SELECT "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_college_count", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "store_returns"."sr_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "store_returns"."sr_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "customer"."c_current_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk"  WHERE CAST("store_returns"."sr_return_quantity" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%16.0%' AND "customer"."c_birth_country" != 'MOLDOVA, REPUBLIC OF' AND "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" IN (7, 10, 9, 6, 5) GROUP BY "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_college_count" ORDER BY "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_college_count";

SELECT "customer_demographics"."cd_purchase_estimate", "household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer_demographics" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_ship_cdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk"  WHERE "customer_demographics"."cd_purchase_estimate" = 1500 GROUP BY "customer_demographics"."cd_purchase_estimate", "household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count" ORDER BY "customer_demographics"."cd_purchase_estimate", "household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count";

SELECT "promotion"."p_promo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "store_sales"."ss_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "promotion" ON "store_sales"."ss_promo_sk" = "promotion"."p_promo_sk"  WHERE "store_sales"."ss_sold_date_sk" IS NULL GROUP BY "promotion"."p_promo_sk" ORDER BY "promotion"."p_promo_sk";

SELECT "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns"  WHERE "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk" = 6170 AND "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk" IN (2800) AND "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" != 139 AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%15.0%' GROUP BY "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk" ORDER BY "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk";

SELECT "warehouse"."w_gmt_offset", "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "warehouse" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk"  WHERE ("warehouse"."w_gmt_offset" IN (-5.00) OR (CAST("warehouse"."w_gmt_offset" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%-6.0%' AND "warehouse"."w_gmt_offset" = -5.00)) AND (CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%1%.0%' OR "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" IN (3, 2, 4, 5, 6) OR CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%1.%0%') AND CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%7%.0%' GROUP BY "warehouse"."w_gmt_offset", "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" ORDER BY "warehouse"."w_gmt_offset", "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk";

SELECT "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk", "web_page"."wp_max_ad_count", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_bill_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_returning_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_page" ON "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" = "web_page"."wp_web_page_sk"  WHERE CAST("web_sales"."ws_quantity" AS varchar) LIKE '%85.0%' AND ("web_sales"."ws_web_page_sk" != 37 OR "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" IN (5397, 3416, 3375, 4481, 2954, 2167, 6191, 5711, 5666, 6894, 4639, 2477, 1651, 658, 5721, 3086) OR "web_sales"."ws_web_page_sk" IN (127, 91, 49, 217, 79, 1, 187, 61, 85)) GROUP BY "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk", "web_page"."wp_max_ad_count" ORDER BY "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk", "web_page"."wp_max_ad_count";

SELECT "store"."s_number_employees", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "store"."s_store_sk" = "store_sales"."ss_store_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "promotion" ON "store_sales"."ss_promo_sk" = "promotion"."p_promo_sk"  WHERE CAST("store_sales"."ss_net_paid_inc_tax" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.0%' AND CAST("store_sales"."ss_ext_tax" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.0%' GROUP BY "store"."s_number_employees" ORDER BY "store"."s_number_employees";

SELECT "web_site"."web_street_number", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_page"."wp_creation_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "store"."s_closed_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "call_center" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "web_page"."wp_web_page_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_site" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_site"."web_close_date_sk"  WHERE "web_site"."web_open_date_sk" IN (2450526, 2450781, 2450654, 2450807, 2450577, 2450798, 2450747, 2450543, 2450705, 2450730, 2450603, 2450756, 2450696, 2450594, 2450679, 2450645) AND (CAST("call_center"."cc_mkt_desc" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%others%.%' OR ("call_center"."cc_class" != 'medium' AND CAST("call_center"."cc_mkt_desc" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%others%.%')) AND CAST("call_center"."cc_hours" AS varchar) LIKE '%8AM-%8AM%' AND "date_dim"."d_day_name" != 'Friday' GROUP BY "web_site"."web_street_number" ORDER BY "web_site"."web_street_number";

SELECT "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk", "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns"  WHERE "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" != 28 AND "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk" != 4970 AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_account_credit" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.0%' AND "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" IN (91, 43, 67, 55, 217, 109, 199) GROUP BY "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk", "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity" ORDER BY "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk", "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_qoy", COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "date_dim"  WHERE CAST("date_dim"."d_day_name" AS varchar) LIKE '%Monda%y%' GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_qoy" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_qoy";

SELECT "store_sales"."ss_quantity", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "store_sales"."ss_sold_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "store_sales"."ss_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "item"."i_item_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_item_sk"  WHERE CAST("time_dim"."t_second" AS varchar) LIKE '%3%5%' AND "catalog_sales"."cs_promo_sk" IN (370, 209) AND CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_ship_mode_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%14.0%' GROUP BY "store_sales"."ss_quantity" ORDER BY "store_sales"."ss_quantity";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_open_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "store"."s_closed_date_sk"  WHERE CAST("store"."s_suite_number" AS varchar) LIKE '%270%' AND (CAST("web_sales"."ws_ext_ship_cost" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.0%' OR CAST("web_sales"."ws_ext_ship_cost" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.0%') AND CAST("web_sales"."ws_ship_mode_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%19.0%' AND "date_dim"."d_qoy" = 2;

SELECT "call_center"."cc_rec_end_date", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "date_dim" LEFT OUTER JOIN "call_center" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_page" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "catalog_page"."cp_start_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_sold_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_sold_date_sk"  WHERE "date_dim"."d_current_year" = 'Y' AND "date_dim"."d_moy" = 1 AND CAST("call_center"."cc_gmt_offset" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%-6.0%' GROUP BY "call_center"."cc_rec_end_date" ORDER BY "call_center"."cc_rec_end_date";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "income_band" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_bill_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "promotion" ON "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" = "promotion"."p_promo_sk"  WHERE (CAST("web_sales"."ws_quantity" AS varchar) LIKE '%2%2.0%' OR CAST("web_sales"."ws_sales_price" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.%0%') AND "household_demographics"."hd_dep_count" IN (5, 0, 6, 4, 3, 8, 1) AND "web_sales"."ws_bill_hdemo_sk" IN (5008) AND ("promotion"."p_start_date_sk" != 2450853 OR ("promotion"."p_start_date_sk" IN (2450299, 2450347, 2450711, 2450849, 2450296) AND "promotion"."p_start_date_sk" IN (2450337, 2450853, 2450900, 2450347, 2450241, 2450849, 2450740))) AND "web_sales"."ws_ship_mode_sk" != 15;

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "warehouse" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_warehouse_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "web_sales"."ws_bill_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_bill_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk"  WHERE "customer_address"."ca_street_type" IN ('Wy', 'Street', 'Dr.') AND (CAST("customer"."c_birth_month" AS varchar) LIKE '%1.0%' OR "customer"."c_birth_month" != 11) AND ("warehouse"."w_suite_number" IS NOT NULL OR "warehouse"."w_suite_number" IN ('Suite P', 'Suite 470', 'Suite X') OR CAST("warehouse"."w_suite_number" AS varchar) LIKE '%Suite%');

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "household_demographics" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_site" ON "web_sales"."ws_web_site_sk" = "web_site"."web_site_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "store_returns"."sr_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk"  WHERE ("store_returns"."sr_returned_date_sk" IN (2451193, 2451206, 2452299, 2451208, 2451562) OR "store_returns"."sr_returned_date_sk" IN (2451193, 2451187, 2451562, 2451570, 2452301, 2451558, 2451208, 2452299, 2451185, 2451199, 2452298, 2451206, 2451198, 2451554, 2452294, 2452303) OR "store_returns"."sr_returned_date_sk" IN (2451570, 2452303)) AND "customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" IN ('High Risk');

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "ship_mode" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_mode_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk"  WHERE ("ship_mode"."sm_type" != 'OVERNIGHT' OR CAST("ship_mode"."sm_type" AS varchar) LIKE '%D%AY%' OR "ship_mode"."sm_type" IN ('LIBRARY', 'REGULAR')) AND "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_mode_sk" IN (10, 3, 6, 1, 17, 4, 14, 16, 18);

SELECT "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_hdemo_sk", "item"."i_manufact_id", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "store_returns"."sr_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_addr_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_bill_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "store_returns"."sr_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE "catalog_sales"."cs_bill_hdemo_sk" IN (274, 1758, 5817, 5920, 6172, 3783, 606, 1479, 2955, 1888, 4804) AND (CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_warehouse_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%4%.0%' OR (CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_warehouse_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%5.0%' AND CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_warehouse_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%4.0%')) AND "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_hdemo_sk" IN (243, 4804, 3783, 26, 681) AND CAST("item"."i_class_id" AS varchar) LIKE '%1%.0%' GROUP BY "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_hdemo_sk", "item"."i_manufact_id" ORDER BY "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_hdemo_sk", "item"."i_manufact_id";

SELECT "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk", "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "income_band" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_hdemo_sk"  WHERE "income_band"."ib_lower_bound" != 180001 GROUP BY "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk", "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk" ORDER BY "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk", "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk";

SELECT "catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk", "customer"."c_first_name", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "reason" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "reason"."r_reason_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk"  WHERE "catalog_returns"."cr_returned_date_sk" IN (2451252, 2451979, 2451619, 2451250, 2451983, 2451625, 2451974, 2451988, 2451615, 2452339, 2451253, 2451985, 2451977) AND "catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" IS NOT NULL AND "reason"."r_reason_sk" IN (3, 29, 17, 34, 18, 11, 8, 16, 22, 30, 35, 27, 7, 19) AND "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" IN (4, 6, 3) AND "customer"."c_birth_country" IN ('ITALY', 'CZECH REPUBLIC', 'QATAR', 'PARAGUAY', 'HUNGARY', 'SWEDEN', 'BELIZE', 'TOKELAU', 'BRUNEI DARUSSALAM', 'SPAIN', 'CAMEROON', 'BURUNDI', 'EGYPT', 'MOLDOVA, REPUBLIC OF', 'GUYANA', 'LESOTHO', 'TUVALU') GROUP BY "catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk", "customer"."c_first_name" ORDER BY "catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk", "customer"."c_first_name";
